---
import Layout from "@layouts/Layout.astro";
import Candlestick from "@components/charts/Candlestick.astro";
import dia from "@data/dia.json";
---

<Layout
	metaTitle="Home | Lestoque Report"
	metaDescription="Technical Analysis of Stocks, ETF's and Cryptocurrency."
>
	<h1>Lestoque Report</h1>

	<p class="lead">
		The Definitive Guide to Swing Trading in Market-Leading Sectors and
		Securities!
	</p>

	<h2>📈 Mastering Swing Trading Strategies:</h2>
	<Candlestick priceData={JSON.stringify(dia)} />
	<p>
		Embark on a journey to master the art of swing trading with our in-depth
		report. Discover proven strategies tailored for market-leading sectors and
		securities, enabling you to capitalize on short to medium-term price
		movements with precision.
	</p>

	<h2>🌐 Sector-Specific Insights:</h2>
	<p>
		Our report exclusively focuses on market-leading sectors, providing you with
		sector-specific insights and analyses. Stay ahead of the curve by
		understanding the unique dynamics influencing each sector and uncovering
		swing trading opportunities within them.
	</p>

	<h2>📊 Identifying Swing Trade Candidates:</h2>
	<p>
		Uncover potential swing trade candidates with our detailed analysis of
		securities. We meticulously identify securities exhibiting strong technical
		patterns, making it easier for you to pinpoint opportunities for profitable
		swing trades.
	</p>

	<h2>📆 Timely Market Updates:</h2>
	<p>
		Time is money, especially in swing trading. Receive timely updates on
		market-leading sectors and securities, ensuring you're well-informed about
		emerging opportunities and potential risks. Our report keeps you in sync
		with the dynamic nature of swing trading.
	</p>

	<h2>📉 Risk Mitigation in Swing Trading:</h2>
	<p>
		Navigate the complexities of swing trading with confidence using our risk
		mitigation strategies. We don't just focus on potential gains; we guide you
		through effective risk management, helping you protect your capital in the
		volatile world of swing trading.
	</p>

	<h2>🔍 Technical Analysis Unleashed:</h2>
	<p>
		Gain a deep understanding of technical analysis as we break down complex
		chart patterns and indicators. Our report demystifies technical jargon,
		providing you with the knowledge needed to make informed decisions in
		real-time.
	</p>

	<h2>💡 Expert Commentary on Market Trends:</h2>
	<p>
		Benefit from expert commentary on market trends and potential swing trade
		opportunities. Our report includes insights from seasoned analysts, offering
		a nuanced perspective on the sectors and securities poised for significant
		moves.
	</p>

	<p>
		Arm yourself with sector-specific knowledge, identify high-potential
		securities, and execute precision swing trades with confidence.
	</p>
</Layout>
